OL,3,CTriple killer Calocane shouldn't have
OL,4,Cbeen discharged to GP, inquiry hears
OL,6,FValdo Calocane's schizophrenia was
OL,7,Feffectively unmanaged and untreated
OL,8,Fafter he was discharged from mental
OL,9,Fhealth services due to non-engagement,
OL,10,Fa public inquiry has heard.
OL,12,FThe former mechanical engineering
OL,13,Fstudent had been under the care of
OL,14,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,15,FFoundation Trust for two years, during
OL,16,Fwhich time a consultant psychiatrist
OL,17,Fwarned that he would end up killing
OL,18,Fsomeone.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
