OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778695868
OL,3,CTriple killer Calocane shouldn't have
OL,4,Cbeen discharged to GP, inquiry hears
OL,6,FHe was discharged by the trust's Early
OL,7,FIntervention in Psychosis service in
OL,8,FSeptember 2022, nine months before he
OL,9,Fkilled three people and tried to kill
OL,10,Fthree others, because he failed to
OL,11,Fturn up for appointments or make
OL,12,Fcontact with the team.
OL,14,FCalocane, who was diagnosed with
OL,15,Fparanoid schizophrenia in 2020, killed
OL,16,FUniversity of Nottingham students
OL,17,FBarnaby Webber and Grace O'Malley-
OL,18,FKumar, both 19, and grandfather Ian
OL,19,FCoates, 65, before running over three
OL,20,Fpedestrians with a van in a violent
OL,21,Frampage in the city in June 2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
