OL,3,CTriple killer Calocane shouldn't have
OL,4,Cbeen discharged to GP, inquiry hears
OL,6,FGiving evidence at the Nottingham
OL,7,FInquiry in central London, Dr Tim
OL,8,FBaker, a GP and partner at the
OL,9,FUniversity of Nottingham's Cripps
OL,10,FHealth Centre, where Calocane was a
OL,11,Fpatient from September 2017, said it
OL,12,Fwas his view that the triple killer
OL,13,Fshould not have been discharged from
OL,14,Fmental health services.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778695868
OL,3,CTriple killer Calocane shouldn't have
OL,4,Cbeen discharged to GP, inquiry hears
OL,6,FIn his statement for the inquiry, Dr
OL,7,FBaker, who never had any interactions
OL,8,Fwith Calocane, said he would expect a
OL,9,Fpatient to be discharged from
OL,10,Fsecondary care "only when and if it
OL,11,Fwas considered safe to do so" and that
OL,12,Fdischarges from secondary care are
OL,13,F"specialist decisions based on careful
OL,14,Freview of diagnosis, risk and safety".
OL,26,@rD@POUsD@]O]uD@AOUvD@eO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
