PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778695868
OL,3,CTriple killer Calocane shouldn't have
OL,4,Cbeen discharged to GP, inquiry hears
OL,6,F"Neither in the discharge letter or in
OL,7,Fany of the correspondence your
OL,8,Fpractice received is there any
OL,9,Fsuggestion that the discharge was
OL,10,Fbased on any assessment of safety,
OL,11,Fsimply that he had disengaged?"
OL,12,Fcounsel to the inquiry Craig Carr
OL,13,Fasked.
OL,15,F"That's correct," Dr Baker responded.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@_O]wD@AOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
