OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778695868
OL,3,CTriple killer Calocane shouldn't have
OL,4,Cbeen discharged to GP, inquiry hears
OL,6,FMr Carr said: "Someone lacking in
OL,7,Finsight, nonconcordant (with taking
OL,8,Fmedication), known to be violent when
OL,9,Fnot medicated ` is it your view that
OL,10,Fthat is the kind of patient who should
OL,11,Fnot be discharged to primary care on
OL,12,Fthe grounds of non-engagement?
OL,14,F"Dr Baker replied: "Yes, that is my
OL,15,Fview."Asked if the doctor's surgery,
OL,16,Fwhich has 44,000 patients and 20 GPs,
OL,17,Fhad a mechanism to allow for the
OL,18,Fpotential that secondary care had made
OL,19,Fa wrong decision, Dr Baker said: "In
OL,20,Freality, general practice is very busy
OL,21,Fdoing general practice.
OL,26,@nD@OOUvD@AO]vD@TOUwD@FO]{D@bOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
