PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778695868
OL,3,CTriple killer Calocane shouldn't have
OL,4,Cbeen discharged to GP, inquiry hears
OL,6,F"We put a lot of trust in our
OL,7,Fspecialist colleagues, in all
OL,8,Fspecialities, to do their job and
OL,9,Fensure that when they discharge
OL,10,Fsomeone, it is safe and with clear
OL,11,Finstructions for us non-specialists to
OL,12,Fpick up the baton, which was not done
OL,13,Fhere."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
