CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778695868
OL,3,CTriple killer Calocane shouldn't have
OL,4,Cbeen discharged to GP, inquiry hears
OL,6,FTherefore, following his discharge,
OL,7,Fhis mental health was "going to go
OL,8,Funmanaged and untreated", Mr Carr
OL,9,Fsaid, to which the doctor replied:
OL,10,F"Yes."
OL,12,FThe inquiry heard several text
OL,13,Fmessages that were sent to Calocane by
OL,14,Fhis GP went unanswered.Like most
OL,15,Fpatients, text message was Calocane's
OL,16,Fpreferred method of communication, Dr
OL,17,FBaker said, but he admitted that
OL,18,Ftrying to phone him would have been a
OL,19,F"very good option".
OL,26,@oD@WOUpD@XO]rD@AOUrD@FO]{D@AOU{D@RO]
