OL,3,CTriple killer Calocane shouldn't have
OL,4,Cbeen discharged to GP, inquiry hears
OL,6,FThe surgery's reflections on this are
OL,7,Fthat it now uses multiple modes of
OL,8,Fcommunication to contact patients.
OL,10,FThe inquiry continues.
